title: Beautiful West Austin Home - Available Now!
posting_body: Beautiful Pemberton featuring gourmet kitchen with built-in refrigerator, wine refrigerator, Viking range, wall oven, and built-in Miele coffee maker-ideal for entertaining!
Double doors from the kitchen and dining open to a covered, outdoor kitchen/living area.
Spacious primary suite with walk-in closet/dressing room which leads to the primary bath with two sinks, a walk-in shower, and soaking tub.
Two additional bedrooms, laundry, and office on the 2nd floor.
And an unfinished walk-out attic is the whole length of the 3rd floor, which is ideal for large storage.
The elevator conveniently goes to all three floors.
Will consider a 6-24 month lease terms.
Text Seth for more information or to schedule a viewing!
Listing by Kuper Sotheby's Itl Rlty
